 ------
 Performance Tests
 ------

Performance Tests

  Performance tests are executed with {{{https://databene.org/contiperf}ContiPerf}} via JUnit 4.

  They are excluded from the normal test run and must be triggered explicitly:

+--
./mvnw test -Dtest=RestaurantSearchPerformanceTest
+--

  After running them, the raw ContiPerf report is available at:
  {{{./performance/index.html}Direct HTML Report}}.

